@startuml
title Ownership and Borrowing Contract

[*] --> Owned

Owned --> SharedBorrowed : &Molecule
SharedBorrowed --> Owned : readers finish
SharedBorrowed --> SharedBorrowed : add another &Molecule

Owned --> MutablyBorrowed : &mut Molecule
MutablyBorrowed --> Owned : editor finishes

SharedBorrowed --> Forbidden : request &mut Molecule
MutablyBorrowed --> Forbidden : request &Molecule or &mut Molecule
Forbidden --> Owned : compiler rejects code path

state Owned {
  [*] --> Stable
  Stable : molecule has one owner
}

state SharedBorrowed {
  [*] --> ReadOnly
  ReadOnly : many readers allowed
  ReadOnly : no mutation allowed
}

state MutablyBorrowed {
  [*] --> Editing
  Editing : one editor allowed
  Editing : no other readers or editors
}

note right of Forbidden
  This is the teaching contract:
  many readers OR one writer.
end note

@enduml

